metadata.name: GOD IS DEAD
metadata.description:
This digital painting combines photography/photomontage, graphic elements with artificial intelligence (AI) and subsequently refined with light and material effects.

The work "GOD IS DEAD" reflects the blind devotion of various religions, which only lead to demarcation, isolation, monotony and violence. Man is only part of a corrupt and material world hiding under the cloak of divine belief. The individual plays no role and serves only as a product to spread the madness.

2,910 x 3,324 px  
Created by S0ULW1p3R ᴺᶠᵀ in August 2022
